27:23.520 --> 27:26.320
The game show is well remembered for its elaborate theming,

27:26.320 --> 27:29.760
high energy, production value, and talented cast.

27:29.760 --> 27:33.280
It is considered not only one of PBS's greatest children shows,

27:33.280 --> 27:36.160
but one of the greatest game shows created for children.

27:36.160 --> 27:39.760
Impressive considering it aired in the golden age of children's game shows.

27:40.320 --> 27:45.360
Above all, the show had a very specific goal of educating children on geography,

27:45.360 --> 27:49.760
a goal that it achieved and surpassed, resulting in not just education,

27:49.760 --> 27:52.800
but celebration of the world and its cultures.

27:52.800 --> 27:56.800
All of this wrapped inside a humorous, non-stop detective adventure.

27:56.800 --> 27:58.960
It is no wonder that the show was a hit,

